Speaker 1: That's a great idea! I think our neighbors would love that.
Speaker 2: I think so too. Let's chat more about it next time. I got some stuff to take care of in the house.
Speaker 1: Sure thing! Take care and see you around.
Speaker 2: You too, catch you later.
